c: 46
v: 17
t: "But he who says to his parents: \"Fie upon you both! Do you hold out the promise to me that I shall be raised up (again) when generations before me have passed away (without rising)?\" While they (father and mother) invoke Allah for help (and rebuke their son): \"Woe to you! Believe! Verily, the Promise of Allah is true.\" But he says: \"This is nothing but the tales of the ancient"